B2B/Private Store - Pro Plan


Store Actions
Store Products

3 min
purpose this section allows the admin to manage all the products assigned to the store at the time of adding product in the 'assigned' section and enlists only for default store product in the 'unassigned' section manage store products screen at glance the store products tab enlists all the products assigned to the store with available to, product type icon and assign/unassign tab the 'available to' section shows that whether the product is assigned to all store or to a specific store in the 'unassigned' tab, admin can check the list of products not assigned to the store using the assigned toggle button, admin can quickly assign any product to the store the page also contains quick navigation to add products into the system using ' add product' section
